---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Inversiones en Bolivia 2026 — DPF, Bonos TGN, SAFIs y Bienes Raíces"
  description="Guía completa para invertir en Bolivia en 2026. Comparativa de DPF, Bonos TGN, SAFIs, bienes raíces y capital privado. Rendimientos, riesgos, montos mínimos y tributación."
>

<style>
  .hero-bg { background:linear-gradient(135deg,#060F1E 0%,#0A1F42 45%,#0D2860 100%); }
  .gold-bg  { background:linear-gradient(135deg,#D4A843 0%,#A87420 100%); }
  .card     { background:#fff; border-radius:16px; box-shadow:0 2px 18px rgba(10,31,66,.08); }
  .font-mono-num { font-family:'DM Mono','Courier New',monospace; font-weight:500; }
  .badge-gold   { background:rgba(212,168,67,.14);border:1px solid rgba(212,168,67,.40);color:#A87420;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:20px;display:inline-block; }
  .badge-green  { background:#D1FAE5;color:#065F46;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:20px;display:inline-block; }
  .badge-blue   { background:#DBEAFE;color:#1E40AF;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:20px;display:inline-block; }
  .badge-purple { background:#EDE9FE;color:#5B21B6;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:20px;display:inline-block; }
  .badge-red    { background:#FEE2E2;color:#991B1B;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:20px;display:inline-block; }
  .inv-card { border-radius:20px; overflow:hidden; transition:transform .25s,box-shadow .25s; }
  .inv-card:hover { transform:translateY(-4px); box-shadow:0 12px 36px rgba(10,31,66,.16); }
  .ret-bar { height:10px; border-radius:5px; background:#E5EDF8; overflow:hidden; margin:4px 0; }
  .ret-fill { height:100%; border-radius:5px; transition:width .8s cubic-bezier(.34,1.56,.64,1); }
  .risk-bar { height:8px; border-radius:4px; background:#E5EDF8; overflow:hidden; }
  .risk-fill { height:100%; border-radius:4px; }
  .cmp-tbl { width:100%; border-collapse:separate; border-spacing:0; font-size:13px; }
  .cmp-tbl thead th { padding:12px 14px; font-size:10px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.06em; }
  .cmp-tbl thead th:first-child { text-align:left; }
  .cmp-tbl td { padding:12px 14px; border-bottom:1px solid #EDF2F9; }
  .cmp-tbl td:first-child { font-weight:600; color:#4B6A9B; }
  .cmp-tbl tbody tr:last-child td { border-bottom:none; }
  .cmp-tbl tbody tr:hover td { background:#F7FAFF; }
  .tip-box { border-left:4px solid; border-radius:0 12px 12px 0; padding:14px 16px; }
</style>

<section class="hero-bg text-white relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
    <div style="position:absolute;top:-60px;right:-80px;width:420px;height:420px;border-radius:50%;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(212,168,67,.09) 0%,transparent 70%)"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-14 sm:py-20 relative">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
        <span class="badge-gold uppercase">Guía de Inversión 2026</span>
        <span class="badge-green">Mercado Boliviano</span>
        <span class="badge-purple">Más allá del DPF</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mb-4">
        Alternativas de Inversión<br><span class="text-yellow-300">en Bolivia</span><br>más allá del DPF
      </h1>
      <p class="text-blue-200 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
        El Depósito a Plazo Fijo es solo una opción. Conocé las alternativas disponibles para el inversor boliviano, con sus rendimientos, riesgos y liquidez comparados.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="#comparativa" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#D4A843,#A87420);color:#fff;font-weight:700;padding:12px 24px;border-radius:12px;text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(212,168,67,.40);">Ver Comparativa</a>
        <a href="/dpf/calculadora" style="background:transparent;color:white;font-weight:700;padding:12px 24px;border-radius:12px;text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.3);">Calculadora DPF</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="bg-white border-b border-gray-100">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-4 grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
    <div class="text-center"><p class="font-mono-num text-xl font-bold text-navy-900">4</p><p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-0.5">Alternativas reguladas</p></div>
    <div class="text-center border-l border-gray-100"><p class="font-mono-num text-xl font-bold text-yellow-600">7%+</p><p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-0.5">Rendimiento SAFIs referencial</p></div>
    <div class="text-center border-l border-gray-100"><p class="font-mono-num text-xl font-bold text-green-600">UFV</p><p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-0.5">Cobertura inflacionaria</p></div>
    <div class="text-center border-l border-gray-100"><p class="font-mono-num text-xl font-bold text-navy-900">ASFI</p><p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-0.5">Regulador del mercado</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 pt-8">
  <div class="rounded-2xl p-4 flex gap-3 items-start" style="background:rgba(212,168,67,.08);border:1px solid rgba(212,168,67,.25);">
    <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#D4A843" stroke-width="2" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 8v4m0 4h.01"/></svg>
    <p class="text-sm text-yellow-800 leading-relaxed"><strong>Aviso importante:</strong> Esta guía es educativa e informativa. Los rendimientos mencionados son referenciales y no garantizan resultados futuros. Consultá siempre con un asesor financiero antes de invertir.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="py-12 sm:py-16 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
  <div class="text-center mb-12">
    <span class="badge-gold uppercase">Opciones Disponibles</span>
    <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold mt-3">Las 4 principales alternativas</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-500 mt-2 max-w-xl mx-auto">Todas reguladas y disponibles para el inversor boliviano.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">

    <div class="inv-card card p-6" style="border-top:4px solid #0A1F42;">
      <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center" style="background:#EEF4FF;"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1D4ED8" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2v20M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 000 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 010 7H6"/></svg></div>
          <div><h3 class="font-bold text-base text-navy-900">DPF Bancario</h3><p class="text-xs text-slate-400">Depósito a Plazo Fijo</p></div>
        </div>
        <span class="badge-blue">Referencia</span>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-3 mb-5">
        <div><div class="flex justify-between text-xs mb-1"><span class="text-slate-500 font-semibold">Rendimiento anual neto</span><span class="font-mono-num font-bold text-blue-600">2% – 6%</span></div><div class="ret-bar"><div class="ret-fill" style="width:35%;background:#1D4ED8;"></div></div></div>
        <div><div class="flex justify-between text-xs mb-1"><span class="text-slate-500 font-semibold">Riesgo</span><span class="font-mono-num font-bold text-green-600">Muy bajo</span></div><div class="risk-bar"><div class="risk-fill" style="width:15%;background:#22C55E;"></div></div></div>
        <div><div class="flex justify-between text-xs mb-1"><span class="text-slate-500 font-semibold">Liquidez</span><span class="font-mono-num font-bold text-red-500">Baja</span></div><div class="risk-bar"><div class="risk-fill" style="width:20%;background:#EF4444;"></div></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-xs mb-4">
        <div class="p-2 rounded-xl" style="background:#F0F4FB;"><p class="text-slate-400 font-semibold">Monto mínimo</p><p class="font-mono-num font-bold text-navy-900 mt-0.5">Bs. 1,000</p></div>
        <div class="p-2 rounded-xl" style="background:#F0F4FB;"><p class="text-slate-400 font-semibold">Plazo</p><p class="font-bold text-navy-900 mt-0.5">30 a 1,080 días</p></div>
        <div class="p-2 rounded-xl" style="background:#F0F4FB;"><p class="text-slate-400 font-semibold">Impuesto</p><p class="font-bold text-navy-900 mt-0.5">RC-IVA 13%</p></div>
        <div class="p-2 rounded-xl" style="background:#F0F4FB;"><p class="text-slate-400 font-semibold">Cobertura FOPA</p><p class="font-bold text-green-600 mt-0.5">UFV 250,000</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-box text-xs" style="border-color:#1D4ED8;background:#EFF6FF;color:#1E40AF;">La opción más segura y simple. Ideal para el primer paso en inversión.</div>
      <a href="/dpf/calculadora" style="margin-top:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:8px;padding:10px 16px;border-radius:12px;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;border:2px solid #0A1F42;color:#0A1F42;text-decoration:none;background:#fff;transition:all .2s;" onmouseover="this.style.background='#0A1F42';this.style.color='#fff';" onmouseout="this.style.background='#fff';this.style.color='#0A1F42';">Calcular mi DPF</a>
    </div>

    <div class="inv-card card p-6" style="border-top:4px solid #D4A843;">
      <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center gold-bg"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg></div>
          <div><h3 class="font-bold text-base text-navy-900">Bonos del TGN</h3><p class="text-xs text-slate-400">Tesoro General de la Nación</p></div>
        </div>
        <span class="badge-gold">Estado</span>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-3 mb-5">
        <div><div class="flex justify-between text-xs mb-1"><span class="text-slate-500 font-semibold">Rendimiento anual</span><span class="font-mono-num font-bold text-yellow-600">3% – 7%</span></div><div class="ret-bar"><div class="ret-fill" style="width:45%;background:#D4A843;"></div></div></div>
        <div><div class="flex justify-between text-xs mb-1"><span class="text-slate-500 font-semibold">Riesgo</span><span class="font-mono-num font-bold text-green-600">Muy bajo</span></div><div class="risk-bar"><div class="risk-fill" style="width:10%;background:#22C55E;"></div></div></div>
        <div><div class="flex justify-between text-xs mb-1"><span class="text-slate-500 font-semibold">Liquidez</span><span class="font-mono-num font-bold text-yellow-600">Media</span></div><div class="risk-bar"><div class="risk-fill" style="width:45%;background:#F59E0B;"></div></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-xs mb-4">
        <div class="p-2 rounded-xl" style="background:#FFFBEB;"><p class="text-yellow-700 font-semibold">Emisor</p><p class="font-bold text-navy-900 mt-0.5">Estado Boliviano</p></div>
        <div class="p-2 rounded-xl" style="background:#FFFBEB;"><p class="text-yellow-700 font-semibold">Plazo</p><p class="font-bold text-navy-900 mt-0.5">91 a 1,820 días</p></div>
        <div class="p-2 rounded-xl" style="background:#FFFBEB;"><p class="text-yellow-700 font-semibold">Moneda</p><p class="font-bold text-navy-900 mt-0.5">BOB o UFV</p></div>
        <div class="p-2 rounded-xl" style="background:#FFFBEB;"><p class="text-yellow-700 font-semibold">Dónde comprar</p><p class="font-bold text-navy-900 mt-0.5">BCB o bancos</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl text-xs leading-relaxed" style="background:#FFFBEB;border:1px solid rgba(212,168,67,.25);color:#92400E;"><strong>Ventaja clave:</strong> Los bonos en UFV protegen tu inversión contra la devaluación porque su valor se ajusta automáticamente con la inflación.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="inv-card card p-6" style="border-top:4px solid #8B5CF6;">
      <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center" style="background:#EDE9FE;"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#5B21B6" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg></div>
          <div><h3 class="font-bold text-base text-navy-900">Fondos de Inversión (SAFIs)</h3><p class="text-xs text-slate-400">Sociedad Administradora de Fondos</p></div>
        </div>
        <span class="badge-purple">Dinámico</span>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-3 mb-5">
        <div><div class="flex justify-between text-xs mb-1"><span class="text-slate-500 font-semibold">Rendimiento anual referencial</span><span class="font-mono-num font-bold text-purple-600">4% – 12%</span></div><div class="ret-bar"><div class="ret-fill" style="width:65%;background:#8B5CF6;"></div></div></div>
        <div><div class="flex justify-between text-xs mb-1"><span class="text-slate-500 font-semibold">Riesgo</span><span class="font-mono-num font-bold text-yellow-600">Medio</span></div><div class="risk-bar"><div class="risk-fill" style="width:50%;background:#F59E0B;"></div></div></div>
        <div><div class="flex justify-between text-xs mb-1"><span class="text-slate-500 font-semibold">Liquidez</span><span class="font-mono-num font-bold text-green-600">Alta</span></div><div class="risk-bar"><div class="risk-fill" style="width:75%;background:#22C55E;"></div></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-xs mb-4">
        <div class="p-2 rounded-xl" style="background:#F5F3FF;"><p class="text-purple-500 font-semibold">Monto mínimo</p><p class="font-bold text-navy-900 mt-0.5">Desde Bs. 500</p></div>
        <div class="p-2 rounded-xl" style="background:#F5F3FF;"><p class="text-purple-500 font-semibold">Plazo</p><p class="font-bold text-navy-900 mt-0.5">Abierto</p></div>
        <div class="p-2 rounded-xl" style="background:#F5F3FF;"><p class="text-purple-500 font-semibold">Regulador</p><p class="font-bold text-navy-900 mt-0.5">ASFI</p></div>
        <div class="p-2 rounded-xl" style="background:#F5F3FF;"><p class="text-purple-500 font-semibold">Tipos</p><p class="font-bold text-navy-900 mt-0.5">Renta fija / mixto</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl text-xs leading-relaxed" style="background:#F5F3FF;border:1px solid #DDD6FE;color:#5B21B6;"><strong>SAFIs autorizadas en Bolivia:</strong> BISA SAFI, Mercantil Santa Cruz SAFI, Fortaleza SAFI, BNB SAFI, entre otras. Verificá la lista actualizada en asfi.gob.bo.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="inv-card card p-6" style="border-top:4px solid #22C55E;">
      <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center" style="background:#D1FAE5;"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#065F46" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg></div>
          <div><h3 class="font-bold text-base text-navy-900">Bienes Raíces</h3><p class="text-xs text-slate-400">Inversión inmobiliaria</p></div>
        </div>
        <span class="badge-green">Tangible</span>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-3 mb-5">
        <div><div class="flex justify-between text-xs mb-1"><span class="text-slate-500 font-semibold">Rendimiento anual (alquiler)</span><span class="font-mono-num font-bold text-green-600">4% – 8%</span></div><div class="ret-bar"><div class="ret-fill" style="width:50%;background:#22C55E;"></div></div></div>
        <div><div class="flex justify-between text-xs mb-1"><span class="text-slate-500 font-semibold">Riesgo</span><span class="font-mono-num font-bold text-yellow-600">Medio</span></div><div class="risk-bar"><div class="risk-fill" style="width:45%;background:#F59E0B;"></div></div></div>
        <div><div class="flex justify-between text-xs mb-1"><span class="text-slate-500 font-semibold">Liquidez</span><span class="font-mono-num font-bold text-red-500">Muy baja</span></div><div class="risk-bar"><div class="risk-fill" style="width:10%;background:#EF4444;"></div></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-xs mb-4">
        <div class="p-2 rounded-xl" style="background:#F0FDF4;"><p class="text-green-600 font-semibold">Monto mínimo</p><p class="font-bold text-navy-900 mt-0.5">Bs. 100,000+</p></div>
        <div class="p-2 rounded-xl" style="background:#F0FDF4;"><p class="text-green-600 font-semibold">Plazo</p><p class="font-bold text-navy-900 mt-0.5">Largo plazo (5+ años)</p></div>
        <div class="p-2 rounded-xl" style="background:#F0FDF4;"><p class="text-green-600 font-semibold">Ingreso</p><p class="font-bold text-navy-900 mt-0.5">Alquiler mensual</p></div>
        <div class="p-2 rounded-xl" style="background:#F0FDF4;"><p class="text-green-600 font-semibold">Plus-valía</p><p class="font-bold text-navy-900 mt-0.5">3% – 8% anual</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl text-xs leading-relaxed" style="background:#F0FDF4;border:1px solid #BBF7D0;color:#166534;"><strong>Costos ocultos a considerar:</strong> alícuota, impuesto a la propiedad, mantenimiento, períodos vacíos y comisión de inmobiliaria.</div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-12 sm:py-16" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0A1F42 0%,#0D2860 100%);">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-10">
      <span class="badge-gold uppercase">Protección Inflacionaria</span>
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-3">La UFV como instrumento de cobertura</h2>
      <p class="text-blue-300 mt-2">El mecanismo que el BCB diseñó para proteger el valor de tus ahorros</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-white text-base mb-3">¿Qué es la UFV?</h3>
        <p class="text-blue-200 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">La <strong class="text-white">Unidad de Fomento a la Vivienda</strong> es una unidad de cuenta indexada a la inflación, publicada diariamente por el BCB. Su valor se ajusta automáticamente para mantener el poder adquisitivo.</p>
        <div class="rounded-xl p-4" style="background:rgba(212,168,67,.10);border:1px solid rgba(212,168,67,.25);">
          <p class="text-yellow-300 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">Valor actual referencial</p>
          <p class="font-mono-num text-3xl font-bold text-white">Bs. 2.3847 <span class="text-lg text-yellow-300">/ UFV</span></p>
          <p class="text-blue-300 text-xs mt-1">Actualizado diariamente por el BCB</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-white text-base mb-3">¿Cuándo conviene invertir en UFV?</h3>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start"><div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" style="background:rgba(34,197,94,.2);"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#22C55E" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></div><p class="text-blue-200 text-sm">Cuando esperás que la inflación supere la tasa de interés de tu DPF en BOB.</p></div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start"><div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" style="background:rgba(34,197,94,.2);"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#22C55E" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></div><p class="text-blue-200 text-sm">Para ahorros de largo plazo donde querés preservar el poder de compra.</p></div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start"><div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" style="background:rgba(239,68,68,.2);"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#EF4444" stroke-width="3"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></div><p class="text-blue-200 text-sm">No conviene si la inflación es baja — el rendimiento neto puede ser menor al de un DPF en BOB.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="comparativa" class="py-12 sm:py-16 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
  <div class="text-center mb-10">
    <span class="badge-gold uppercase">Comparativa Completa</span>
    <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-semibold mt-3">¿Cuál se adapta a tu perfil?</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-500 mt-2">Todas las opciones en una sola tabla</p>
  </div>
  <div class="card overflow-hidden">
    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="cmp-tbl">
        <thead>
          <tr style="background:#0A1F42;">
